BofA Will Resubmit Application to Fed for Dividend Increase

-- B y   D o n a l   G r i f f i n
-- 
2011-03-18T19:14:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-18/bank-of-america-will-resubmit-application-to-fed-for-a-dividend-increase.html
  Bank of America Corp. (BAC) , the biggest
U.S. lender by assets, will reapply to the  Federal Reserve  for
permission to increase its dividend after June 30, the company
said.  The bank will “resubmit a proposal for a modest dividend
increase in the second half of this year,” said  Scott Silvestri , a spokesman for the  Charlotte , North Carolina-based
company, in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Donal Griffin in  New York  at 
 dgriffin10@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  